name: Maggie & Mi

reviews.text:
If you love Maggie, this is your place to go! They even have fried Maggie cubes which has a cheesy centre! Fish grilled to perfection and chicken cutlet is juicy and tender. The Mash Potatoes and Kani Salad definitely can compare with upscale restaurants.

Friendly staff with good food! Will definitely come back again!!

We ordered the signature chicken chop, wagyu beef and fish cutlet. The maggie + meat combo work better than I thought. The noodle is not too salty and goes well with the soft boiled egg. The meat are of good quality esp. wagyu is juicy. Overall, it's a nice experience, nostalgic maggie mee and eye opening one for young senior like me, ha!

The price is reasonable w/o gst and svc charge. Its value for money.

Had a delicious fish cutlet with buttered corn The portion was generous, and the fish meat was surprisingly moist. Their mala noodles were on point! Fragrant, flavorful, and surprisingly not oily. Paired perfectly with the fish cutlet!
